{"word":"κατίσχω","slug":"κατίσχω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κατίσχω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:collateral'>collat.</a> form of <a href='S:κατέχω'><el>κατέχω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to hold back</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>detinere</el>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to keep by one</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to occupy</i>: <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be occupied</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>III. </b><i>to direct</i> or <i>steer</i> to a place, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>IV. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a>, <i>to come down</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}